text: Amna Suleiman (Arabic: آمنة سليمان) can mean: * Amna Suleiman, teacher and women's bicycle advocate from Gaza featured by BBC 100 Women * Amna Suleiman Abdullah Al-Gharagir, a member of the Jordanian parliament * Amna Suleiman or Amna Jibril, a Palestinian woman from Shatila refugee camp in Beirut, member of the Revolutionary Council of the Fatah movement, and head of the General Union of Palestinian Women in Lebanon
title: Amna Suleiman
